* escape/unescape special chars from headers
* simple monolithic server to get a rough idea of tricky issues
  - fast cleanup on unsubscribe (e.g., currently O(log(n)) of number of destination and O(m) of number of subscribees to a destination)
  - fast cleanup on client death (currently no way of doing it; requires to go through every single subscription)
  - tricky to keep track of sent bytes to a client
